{"tid":1374270,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"爬山裝備集中討論","createTime":"2019-07-27T17:51:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T04:43:01.000Z","uid":286394,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"63b059c8f8eb8af339c2142e082019b4f8e0d77e","tid":1374270,"uid":286394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:51:31.000Z","msg":"想請教下大家有關行山裝備既問題呀，因為試過有次西貢行夜山經過條村，突然遇到勁多惡狗裝兇作勢想撲過黎，個次手上得支弱弱既行山杖差d俾狗咬，野狗有瘋狗症，咬一啖好大獲架嘛，之後有感自己既戶外活動裝備嚴重不足，所以想添下新裝，請教下大家：<br />\n<br />\n淘寶搵到d咁既強光手電筒<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zOv6XvY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzOv6XvY.png&h=e23da0c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u1maEKi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu1maEKi.png&h=50579bf4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">合金材質，又可以伸縮，超強光黑夜唔怕睇唔到路，價格都幾平。照明之餘又可以做基本防衛好似都唔錯，考慮緊買唔買好🤔</span></span><br />\n<br />\n希望各位享受大自然<br />\n同時都好好保護自己<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">爬山撚</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bad690ecf71e74b0f722cfadb71f6496149041e3","tid":1374270,"uid":286394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:54:42.000Z","msg":"爬呀爬"},{"pid":"f295eeabafe4250cc6eed6c0e872622ca18cf6a9","tid":1374270,"uid":286394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:56:24.000Z","msg":"爬啊爬"},{"pid":"0277adaa73a39f0799aa62b6fc11d303e5cc4dd5","tid":1374270,"uid":97997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T18:02:26.000Z","msg":"學術研究，行山仗個頭有冇分咩類型<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gEEjx0t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgEEjx0t.jpg&h=e5022701&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a08551e5f125b60450a43152004084bb33846252","tid":1374270,"uid":286394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,